  "body": "With the most recent jvm-libp2p release, gossip message validation is signaled with a `CompletableFuture<Boolean>` which allows for validation to happen asynchronously.  We should take advantage of this by offloading expensive / time-consuming validations to worker threads.\n\nSee: https://github.com/PegaSysEng/artemis/pull/1044#discussion_r354641985",
